snippet.title: God of the Arena Dungeon | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
God of the Dungeon - Class-based Arena Bullet Hell

Slay vermin, bosses, and other players to become the arena god!

GotAD is developed by our beloved TABG gamer, Gas God IX!

Play now at  http://gotad.io/  or download the client at https://gotad.itch.io/gotadio for class unlocks, server hosting, music and better performance!

Also join the GotAD discord: https://discord.gg/e5FeRdNFHs

All rights reserved 2020 © gotad.io


Credits:

"Mutually Assured Destruction" - Castle Carousel   

https://soundcloud.com/castlecarousel

GotAD Logo by Kupull

Video by SmallWaffles
